This package bundles tokenizer assets derived from official Hugging Face repositories under the Deci organization:
- Deci/DeciCoder-1b tokenizer.json

This package also registers the following official Deci models as aliases of the existing `mistral-7b-v0.1` family provided by `@cyberlangke/tokkit-mistral`:
- Deci/DeciLM-7B
- Deci/DeciLM-7B-instruct

